title: DIED SUDDENLY
cleaned_text:
After tens of millions of people engaged with Died Suddenly, there were numerous questions, criticisms, and deeper rabbit holes to explore to fully explain the depth of what has happened as a result of the Covid-19 vaccination program.

Directors Matthew Skow and Nicholas Stumphauzer are in pre production now on a sequel to address all the criticisms, answer further questions, perform scientific experiments to demonstrate the claims made, and bring all this evidence to Capitol Hill where it belongs.

This is the People of the World vs. The New World Order.
